reviewText: Funny Hood movie on a low budget.  A self-centered- hood detective with no boss, or backup ever.  The bad guys, the knock out weed and, beautiful girls, the love story, deception, beat down,  the crazy twins.  the brothers bent on having a block party, who could ask for more?  And a diverse party. Thumbs up for pulling it off so well
I like the money it was ok it just wasn't that funny n da block party was way better I don't care for part 2 that much I had ordered da block party 3 I hope its better than 2 but the movie was cool

This is lower than low budget. This is no budget.
Besides being an ultra cheap production it also lacks an interesting story and humor.
A waste of time and money.

Just have to say that if you want to watch something where you can laugh, this is the movie! Go ahead!
